 The country's new ministers and deputy ministers will be sworn in at Tuynhuys in Cape Town. #dstv403 • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. CAPE TOWN - The country's new ministers and deputy ministers will be sworn in at Tuynhuys in Cape Town. READ: Kgosientsho Ramokgopa appointed Electricity Minister This follows President Cyril Ramaphosa's announcement to his cabinet on Monday. Paul Mashatile is the new Deputy President while Dr Kgosientsho Ramokgopa was appointed as the new Electricity Minister.